metadata.name: Song of hope
metadata.description:
Sometimes a song can convey many Feeling to the listener. 
Even though we may not understand the song, we can feel the emotion that the song wants to convey.

Sing it a song from your heart

Sing it a song of many feelings

Sing it the song you want to give someone to hear

This is "My Song"

Song No. 1 "Song of Hope"
